<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٠٧٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7010">يَحْيَى بْنُ مُوسَى: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6792">وَكِيعٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6702">هِشَامُ بْنُ عُرْوَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4361">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2065">الزُّبَيْرِ بْنِ الْعَوَّامِ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«لَأَنْ يَأْخُذَ أَحَدُكُمْ أَحْبُلَهُ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>